ram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 512}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am currently by the Loire River in France, having just completed the torch relay.\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 600, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 554, \"end\": 560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999845806957715, \"rank\": 1.109101509743473e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Loire River\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 550}, {\"ngram\": \"the torch relay\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am still very excited and very happy to be here as a young athlete to participate in the event,\\\" Gu said.\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 708, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a young athlete\", \"from\": 654, \"to\": 669}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 697}, {\"ngram\": \"Gu\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 702}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As with every torch relay, this event attracted a large number of local residents who came to cheer on the torchbearers.\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every torch relay\", \"from\": 718, \"to\": 735}, {\"ngram\": \"this event\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 747}, {\"ngram\": \"a large number\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 772}, {\"ngram\": \"local residents\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 791}, {\"ngram\": \"the torchbearers\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 829}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The freestyle ski world champion said the atmosphere deeply moved her, making her even prouder to be a torchbearer.\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 946, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The freestyle ski world champion\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 863}, {\"ngram\": \"the atmosphere\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 883}, {\"ngram\": \"a torchbearer\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I saw children, elderly people, and even babies in their parents' arms along the road.\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 1035, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"children\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 963}, {\"ngram\": \"elderly people\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 979}, {\"ngram\": \"even babies\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 996}, {\"ngram\": \"their parents' arms\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1019}, {\"ngram\": \"the road\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1034}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From them, I could feel their passion for the Olympics and sports.\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1102, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their passion\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1073}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1090}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1101}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think this is also part of the Olympic spirit \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 to attract more people to participate,\\\" said the 20-year-old, who claimed two golds and one silver for China at the 2022 Winter Olympic Games in Beijing.\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1258, \"end\": 1263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9994810616829609, \"rank\": 0.0003358820478930764, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1300, \"end\": 1307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9933444200823391, \"rank\": 0.006700106311847259, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1128}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic spirit\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1150}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1154}, {\"ngram\": \"more people\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1177}, {\"ngram\": \"two golds\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1238}, {\"ngram\": \"one silver\", \"from\": 1243, \"to\": 1253}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2022 Winter Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1296}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the torch relay, Gu frequently made a hand gesture representing the number six.\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1396, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the torch relay\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1332}, {\"ngram\": \"Gu\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1336}, {\"ngram\": \"a hand gesture\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1367}, {\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1391}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She explained to reporters that in Chinese contemporary slang, \\\"six\\\" signifies being awesome.\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1490, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1432, \"end\": 1439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_characters\", \"score\": 0.9920051957573165, \"rank\": 0.008033897589787953, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_characters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_characters\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"reporters\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1423}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally, the gesture resembles horns, and in Chinese, the character \\\"niu,\\\" meaning \\\"cow,\\\" also means awesome or impressive.\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1619, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1541, \"end\": 1548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_characters\", \"score\": 0.9920051957573165, \"rank\": 0.008033897589787953, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_characters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_characters\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gesture\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1516}, {\"ngram\": \"horns\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1532}, {\"ngram\": \"the character\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1563}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"cow\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1583}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wanted to use this gesture to show that China is awesome, and Chinese athletes are awesome too.\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1664, \"end\": 1669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9994810616829609, \"rank\": 0.0003358820478930764, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1686, \"end\": 1693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_characters\", \"score\": 0.9920051957573165, \"rank\": 0.008033897589787953, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_characters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_characters\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this gesture\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I especially hope to see Chinese athletes achieve great results in the upcoming Olympics next month,\\\" said Gu.\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1830, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1745, \"end\": 1752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_characters\", \"score\": 0.9920051957573165, \"rank\": 0.008033897589787953, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_characters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_characters\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"great results\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1783}, {\"ngram\": \"the upcoming Olympics\", \"from\": 1787, \"to\": 1808}, {\"ngram\": \"Gu\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1829}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will definitely come to Paris to watch the Olympics then.\\\"\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1892, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1858, \"end\": 1863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999995982642201, \"rank\": 4.0173587190081287e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1885}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a winter sports athlete, Gu would not be drawn on which event she was most looking forward to at the summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 2014, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a winter sports athlete\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 1920}, {\"ngram\": \"Gu\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 1924}, {\"ngram\": \"which event\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 1958}, {\"ngram\": \"the summer Olympics\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2013}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can not say that.\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2036, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have many friends competing in the Olympics, and if I mention one and forget another, they might not be happy,\\\" Gu joked.\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2160, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many friends\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2056}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2082}, {\"ngram\": \"another\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2123}, {\"ngram\": \"Gu\", \"from\": 2151, \"to\": 2153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With her semester at Stanford University having ended, Gu revealed that she had flown for more than 10 hours to France the day before the torch relay and was completing her final assignments on the plane.\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2366, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2183, \"end\": 2202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_University\", \"score\": 0.9999864884156213, \"rank\": 1.3498525636753955e-05, \"text\": \"Stanford University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_University\"}, {\"begin\": 2274, \"end\": 2280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999845806957715, \"rank\": 1.109101509743473e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phra